title: Zlatan Ibrahimovic: This is the mood inside the Man United camp after Saint-Etienne win
text:
the mood inside the Man United camp after Saint-Etienne win ZLATAN IBRAHIMOVIC insists Manchester United are in a 'decisive moment' in their season. PUBLISHED: 22:13,  19, Thu, Feb 16, 2017 GETTY Zlatan Ibrahimovic thinks Manchester United are in a good moment 
Zlatan Ibrahimovic was the hero for Manchester United in their 3-0 dismantling of Saint-Etienne in the first leg of their last-32 tie at Old Trafford earlier this evening. 
More to follow
